## 6. Demo Flow (Must Work)

1. Visit suspicious site

   * trust score appears

2. Show Gemini explanation

3. Trigger voice alert

4. Attempt login

   * phishing warning appears

5. Open extension popup

   * see stats + trackers blocked

---

## 7. Constraints

* Do NOT overbuild
* Avoid complex sandboxing
* Keep responses fast
* Ensure demo reliability

---

## 8. Success Criteria

The project is complete if:

* trust score works
* Gemini returns summaries
* login warning triggers
* voice alert plays
* dashboard shows stats

---

## 9. Future Extensions (Optional)

* advanced tracking detection
